#ENCRYPTION
openssl des  -a -salt -in large_file.txt -k "abc123" -out large_file.txt.enc

des    => enc algo {use list-ciphers to get a list and then use any}
-in    => input file (plain)
-out   => out file (enc)
-k     => password
-salt  => ovbious
-a     => base64 (easier to email .. gmail does not complain about it)

DECRYPTION
openssl des  -a -d -salt -in large_file.txt -k "abc123" -out large_file.txt.enc

-d     => decrypt

